title: Corn Casserole

instructions: Heat butter in 9x9 inch baking dish until melted, tilting dish to cover bottom. Mix cream-style corn, whole kernel corn, muffin mix and sour cream in bowl. Add to prepared dish and mix well. Bake at 350Â° for 1 hr or until set and brown.
